        <h2 class="section-title">My Resume</h2>
        <p class="resume-description">
          Want to learn more about my experience and background? Check out my resume for a detailed overview of my skills and professional history.
        </p>
        <a href="https://teerapat-prommarak-resume-2023.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resume-button">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="resume-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
